---
source: tests/cli.rs
expression: help
---
List, add, or remove emoji reactions

Usage: reactions <COMMAND>

Commands:
  list    List aggregate reactions and the authenticated account's reaction state
  add     Add one emoji reaction to an activity record
  remove  Remove one emoji reaction from an activity record
  help    Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help
          Print help
